Harry Royston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Royston 0 Harry Royston was a British stage and film actor. He appeared in more than sixty short and feature films during the silent era including Lady Jennifer. Harry_Royston was a_British_stage_and_film_actor .
